description: 햇살이 쏟아지는 교실 창가, 써니(SUNNY)가 턱을 괴고 밖을 보다가 카메라를 발견하고 장난스럽게 윙크합니다. 그녀의 주변으로 무지개색 프리즘 빛이 춤을 추며 교실의 먼지들이 반짝이는 가루로 변합니다.
visual_concept: Bright, high-key classroom setting with large windows letting in intense golden sunlight. A playful girl with a strawberry blonde bob sits at a desk, surrounded by floating dust motes that sparkle like glitter. Rainbow lens flares and prism effects dance across the frame. The atmosphere is vibrant, warm, and full of youthful energy.
camera_movement: handheld style tracking shot moving closer, reacting to the wink
lighting: Strong natural sunlight diffusing through sheer curtains, creating a soft bloom effect
